    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef mince </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong>, <strong>diced</strong> <strong>apricots</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley stalks</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Mix thoroughly with clean hands, then divide the mixture and shape into 3 <strong>meatballs</strong> per person – these are your <strong>harissa beef meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/599.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/599.-step-3-x400.jpg",
