            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/599.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>harissa beef</strong> <strong>meatballs</strong> to one side of your reserved baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the other side, then put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the pepper has softened – these are your <strong>harissa beef meatballs</strong> and <strong>roasted pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1633341284899-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
