            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>harissa paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a large heatproof bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong>, cover and set aside to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1633341311622-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
