            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> with a fork, season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and mix most of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> through (save some for garnish!)</p><p>Once done, add the <strong>roasted pepper </strong>to the couscous and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>roasted pepper couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
